00:19:01.349 --> 00:19:03.184 position:50% align:center
All 'em critters is
back in the oasis,

00:19:03.268 --> 00:19:04.477 position:50% align:center
so they ain't got no dang reason

00:19:04.561 --> 00:19:06.229 position:50% align:center
to go and raid our
taters no more.

00:19:06.312 --> 00:19:07.772 position:50% align:center
Everything's peachy.

00:19:07.856 --> 00:19:09.649 position:50% align:center
If we knew their
bellies was rumblin',

00:19:09.733 --> 00:19:12.652 position:50% align:center
we coulda just slid 'em over
some taters, doncha know?

00:19:12.736 --> 00:19:13.820 position:50% align:center
[whistle blows]

00:19:13.903 --> 00:19:15.071 position:50% align:center
Well, I'm glad you got
to see your folks.

00:19:15.155 --> 00:19:16.239 position:50% align:center
[JUGGERNAUT]
Me, too.

00:19:16.322 --> 00:19:17.574 position:50% align:center
And the potatoes were
doing really good!

00:19:17.657 --> 00:19:19.826 position:50% align:center
I wanted way more adventure.

00:19:19.909 --> 00:19:21.786 position:50% align:center
I want more giggle gas.

00:19:21.870 --> 00:19:23.079 position:50% align:center
[whistle blows]

00:19:24.080 --> 00:19:26.374 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
That girl from my dream...

00:19:28.043 --> 00:19:31.004 position:50% align:center
