by all this evaporating water.

00:19:31.087 --> 00:19:33.548 position:50% align:center
And it looked like
she was crying.

00:19:35.717 --> 00:19:39.846 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA] Amaterasu...
I wonder who she really is.

00:19:40.889 --> 00:19:42.557 position:50% align:center
If it's true that there's
actually someone

00:19:42.640 --> 00:19:44.809 position:50% align:center
inside Amaterasu,

00:19:44.893 --> 00:19:46.394 position:50% align:center
it means there's a contradiction

00:19:46.478 --> 00:19:48.355 position:50% align:center
in the scripture of
the Holy Sol Temple,

00:19:48.438 --> 00:19:51.649 position:50% align:center
which has guided
the Tokyo Empire.

00:19:51.733 --> 00:19:54.277 position:50% align:center
Remember what the prologue says?

00:19:54.361 --> 00:19:59.074 position:50% align:center
"Many years ago, mankind
faced a divine fury."

00:20:03.995 --> 00:20:07.957 position:50% align:center
[LICHT] Many years ago,
mankind faced a divine fury.

00:20:08.041 --> 00:20:10.919 position:50% align:center
In an event known as
the Day of the Cataclysm,

00:20:11.002 --> 00:20:13.630 position:50% align:center
