00:20:30.980 --> 00:20:34.818 position:50% align:center
A man who would later be
known as Raffles the 1st.

00:20:34.901 --> 00:20:37.362 position:50% align:center
Raffles and his disciples
embarked on a quest

00:20:37.445 --> 00:20:40.281 position:50% align:center
to find new light, and they did.

00:20:40.365 --> 00:20:44.119 position:50% align:center
What Raffles found was
an unsullied flame.

00:20:44.202 --> 00:20:47.372 position:50% align:center
The spark that would
kindle an empire.

00:20:53.503 --> 00:20:56.089 position:50% align:center
[LICHT] Raffles saw at once
that the unsullied flame

00:20:56.172 --> 00:20:58.008 position:50% align:center
was a gift from the Great Sol.

00:20:58.091 --> 00:21:01.052 position:50% align:center
He resolved to harness its
power with technology

00:21:01.136 --> 00:21:03.805 position:50% align:center
