00:21:03.888 --> 00:21:06.391 position:50% align:center
By the light of
Amaterasu's sacred flame,

00:21:06.474 --> 00:21:08.727 position:50% align:center
the people began to rebuild.

00:21:08.810 --> 00:21:13.648 position:50% align:center
With its power, they established
a new state in the Far East.

00:21:28.329 --> 00:21:30.415 position:50% align:center
Catch you guys later!

