[bell chimes]

00:21:52.604 --> 00:21:55.023 position:50% align:center
[ANNOUNCER A] Currently,
Amaterasu is operating

00:21:55.106 --> 00:21:57.192 position:50% align:center
at full efficiency.

00:22:01.446 --> 00:22:03.239 position:50% align:center
[SHINRA]
Amaterasu was a driving force

00:22:03.323 --> 00:22:05.825 position:50% align:center
